     Removes all extended permissions granted to a user or group in an ACL object
<p/>
You must execute either the <code>save</code>, <code>saveAsNew</code>, or <code>checkin</code> method to commit
the granted permission to a repository. You must execute either <code>revert</code>, <code>cancelCheckout</code>,
or <code>destory</code> method to discard changes made to an ACL object.
