                          by the query
@param oneAuditPerBatch   Generate one audit trail per batch size; the server only honors this flag 
                          if the caller has Audit Config privilege.
@param oneEventPerBatch   Combines object creation events into a dm_batch_flush event to reduce the 
                          number of events generated during object creation.
@param options            Database-specific options
@throws DfException       Thrown if the operation fails
//@see #com.documentum.fc.client.IDfQuery.setFlushBatchQuery

