IDfId idObj = sess.getIdByQualification("dm_document where r_object_id='0900d5bb8001f900'");
if (idObj.getId().equals("0900d5bb8001f900"))
{
     // Successfully fetched id...
}
</PRE></BLOCKQUOTE><HR>

@param qualification a DQL qualification consisting of that portion of a SELECT statement beginning with the
                     keyword FROM. The DQL qualification uniquely identifies an object in a repository.

