     Retrieves the work items assigned to the specified user.

@param userName             the user whose tasks you want to retrieve
@param filter               can be: {@link #DF_TASKS} or 1 to retrieve only tasks, {@link #DF_NOTIFICATIONS} or 2
                            to retrieve only notifications, {@link #DF_TASKS_AND_NOTIFICATIONS} or 3 to retrieve
                            both tasks and notifications.
@param additionalAttributes the DQL query specifying the additional task attributes that you would like
                            retrieved
@param orderBy              the task attribute used to order the retrieved tasks

