 In order to access the full functionality of the returned content collection you should cast the result
 to {@link IDfContentCollection} or call getCollectionForContentEx4.

 @return a collection containing the object's content in the repository.
 @param	format	specifies the format in which you want the content.
 @param	pageNumber	Identifies the position of the content when the object has
						multiple contents; otherwise, use 0.
 @exception DfException if a server error occurs.

