@param insertAfterNode An IDfVirtualDocumentNode object identifying the node
that will immediately precede the new node in the display
@param nodeToAdd An IDfVirtualDocumentNode object identifying the node you
are adding
@return An IDfVirtualDocumentNode object for the new node
@exception DfException if the server returns an error

     Returns an interface to the DfProperties object owned by this virtual document.
