parsed using the given pattern (also specified in String form).
<p/>
The date string is parsed using the given pattern. If <code>interpretAsJavaPatternOnly</code> is true then the
given pattern is interpretted as a Java pattern; otherwise calling this constructor is equivalent to calling
{@link #DfTime(String, String)} which means the pattern could be either a Docbase date pattern or a Java date
pattern.

